+import {
+    Genres,
+    SEARCH_MOVIE,
+    SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST,
+    SEARCH_POPULAR_MOVIE_LIST,
+} from '../reducers/types';
 
+export const Types = {
+    SEARCH_MOVIE: 'SEARCH_MOVIE',
+    SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_REQUEST: 'SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_REQUEST',
+    SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_SUCCESS: 'SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_SUCCESS',
+    SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_FAILED: 'SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_FAILED',
+    SEARCH_POPULAR_MOVIE_LIST_REQUEST: 'SEARCH_POPULAR_MOVIE_LIST_REQUEST',
+    SEARCH_POPULAR_MOVIE_LIST_SUCCESS: 'SEARCH_POPULAR_MOVIE_LIST_SUCCESS',
+    SEARCH_GENRE_REQUEST: 'SEARCH_GENRER_REQUEST',
+    SEARCH_GENRE_SUCCESS: 'SEARCH_GENRER_SUCCESS',
+};
+
+export const Creators = {
+    searchMovie: ({ movieName }: Omit<SEARCH_MOVIE, 'type'>): SEARCH_MOVIE => ({
+        type: 'SEARCH_MOVIE',
+        movieName,
+    }),
+    searchMovieListRequest: (genre: number) => ({
+        type: 'SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_REQUEST',
+        genre,
+    }),
+    searchPopularMovieListRequest: () => ({
+        type: 'SEARCH_POPULAR_MOVIE_LIST_REQUEST',
+    }),
+
+    searchMovieListSuccess: ({
+        movieList,
+        genre,
+    }: Omit<SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST, 'type'>) => ({
+        type: 'SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_SUCCESS',
+        genre,
+        movieList,
+    }),
+    searchPopularMovieListSuccess: ({
+        popularMovieList,
+    }: Omit<SEARCH_POPULAR_MOVIE_LIST, 'type'>) => ({
+        type: 'SEARCH_POPULAR_MOVIE_LIST_SUCCESS',
+
+        popularMovieList,
+    }),
+
+    searchMovieListFailed: () => ({
+        type: 'SEARCH_MOVIE_LIST_FAILED',
+    }),
+    searchGenrerRequest: () => ({
+        type: 'SEARCH_GENRER_REQUEST',
+    }),
+    searchGenrerSucess: (genreList: Genres[]) => ({
+        type: 'SEARCH_GENRER_SUCCESS',
+        genreList,
+    }),
+};
